column5: we leave for pickle lake in 5 days and i've talked with two guys who were in the area and they all commented about the lack of mosquitos!! any confirmatory experience? musta been the lack of snow this past winter coupled with not alot of rain. phish
no-see-m's took there place, I was there 3 weeks ago.Paul
Yeah, the Pickle Lake area has less bugs this year so far.... knock on wood....
